 44→        <h1>Start Coding in 60 Seconds</h1>
 45→        <p class="hero-subtitle">Zero configuration. One command to build.</p>
 46→        <p class="hero-description">
 47→          Our Docker toolchains include cross-assemblers and build tools for every platform.
 48→          No dependency management. No version conflicts. Just code.
 49→        </p>
 50→      </div>
